{
  "id": "adv_main_01_01_01",
  "title": "星見編1章2話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈の事故から三年）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Three years have passed since Mana’s accident.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}、いるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ you there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "決めたぞ、この子で行く――履歴書だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve settled on this girl. Here’s her resume.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "決めたんですね\nでも履歴書はいいです、面接で判断します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’ve found someone.\nI don’t need to see her resume. I’ll decide based on the audition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうしたいなら止めないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s what you want‚ I won’t stop you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "間違いなく面接の時に腰抜かすからな、覚悟しとけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure you will get surpirsed when she walks into the room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.900000000000006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さんは、この星見プロダクションの社長だ）\n（東京の大手芸能事務所バンプロダクションから独立）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Saegusa-san is the president of Hoshimi Productions.）\n（He started off at a major Tokyo talent agency \"Van Production\"‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.50000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（そしてこの星見市に小さな事務所を立ち上げ）\n（麻奈を発掘した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（before branching off to establish this small talent agency in Hoshimi.）\n（He’s the one who discovered Mana.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それから、今度の新人だが、全てお前に預ける",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I’m leaving this latest batch of newcomers to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.99652180107692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お前もそろそろ、そういう時期だ。じゃあ後でな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you’re ready for the responsibility. Catch you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.39652180107692,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4303.4781989230805,
          "startTime": 43.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈のためにも、新たなアイドルを育て、いつか）\n（再開されるNEXT VENUSグランプリで勝とう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（To honor Mana’s memory‚ we would train more new idols.）\n（And‚ someday‚ our idols would win the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.57712096640935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さんと約束してから、もう三年だ）\n（なのに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s been three years since Saegusa-san and I made a pact about that.）\n（But…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.24378763307602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なんで、あなたはここにいるんですかね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.74378763307602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 59.355692492618864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "顔を近づけるな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t get so up close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.355692492618864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "いいでしょ、どうせ幽霊なんだから\n触れないんだし、ほらキスキス",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the big deal? I’m a ghost‚ after all.\nIt’s not like I can touch you. C'mon‚ Kiss? Kiss?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.28902587363592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あのな……聞いてただろ\n午後から面接なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Knock it off. You were listening‚ weren’t you?\nI have an audition to run this afternoon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.96099881598823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "えーーーっ？\n退屈ー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhhhhhh?\nBoring!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.39433214932157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "全く、最初にお願いしてきた時は\nあんなに殊勝だったのに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My goodness. Wonder what happened to that admirable girl\nwho asked me to join?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.87086279659941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "それ言ったら{user}くんだって\nあの頃はかしこまって話してたでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look at yourself‚ too‚ {user}.\nYou used to treat me with such admiration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.30419612993273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれは……気を遣ってたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ I was just being nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.16651686640908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、赤くなってる\n恥ずかしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah! You’re blushing.\nAre you shy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.59189108821084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "うるさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shut up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.09189108821084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……ということは今、お互いやっと\n普段の自分でぶつかりあえている訳だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Well‚ I guess this just means our relationship evolved‚\nand we can finally be our true selves around each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.98191378724904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（相変わらず可愛い――俺はすでに二十二歳だが）\n（麻奈の姿は死んだ時のままだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana is as cute as ever. I’m already 22‚ ）\n（Meanwhile‚ the clock stopped for her the day she died.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.78191378724908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "俺は昔の、麻奈の方が好きだったけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Too bad. I preferred the Mana at that time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.28191378724908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "酷い！　素顔のトップアイドルだよ\nレアでしょ？　レア",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unbelievable! You get to see a top idol in all her natural glory.\nThat’s a rarity‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.45728785010516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、最初に幽霊として現れた時は\n驚いたし、嬉しかったさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah‚ I was surprised and happy\nwhen you first came back as a ghost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.95457183432232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、考えてみたら俺だけに見えても\nどうしようもないというか、むしろうるさいというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But ‚I’m the only one who can see you.\nThat doesn't really help and rather that’s kind of… pointless? Annoying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.12634854886653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "酷くない？　死んだ霊が\nやり残したことがあるって、わざわざ会いに来たんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That hurts‚ I came all the way back\nas a ghost here and trusted you to give me closure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.11549077914097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "そのやり残したっていうのは\nあの決勝のステージに立つことなんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ and this “closure” you want\nIt’s to perform at the finals‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0728323686715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあそうでしょう？　あれだけ賭けてたのよ\nあのステージに立たない限り、成仏出来ない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I poured my heart and soul into getting there.\nUntil I perform on that stage‚ I can’t possibly move on to the afterlife!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.10616570200477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは鼻息出さない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols don't breathe through their noses so hard like you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8323673249899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
