      "text": "仕方ないでしょ、決勝は結局中止になっちゃって\nその後はグランプリ自体開かれていないんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I supposed to do? The finals got canceled‚\nand the Grand Prix itself hasn’t been held since.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.60617694870803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
